  "texts": [
    "Leisure Activities:Five studies from the list of remaining studies were in the IADL category of leisure activities.",
    "Three of them were using home healthcare technologies [83,127,130] for leisure activities for older adults, and other two studies offered robot technologies [65,84] to older adults.",
    "For home healthcare technologies, computerized programs via tablet and remote monitoring were provided to participants to promote active wellbeing for the older adults.",
    "For the studies with robot technologies, companion robots were used for keeping older adults physically and mentally fit in their home environments.",
    "Communication Activities:Communication activities are the second most targeted IADLs in remaining studies (n=20)."
  ],
